query:
SELECT 
  ar.id, ar.name, ar.version, ar.constructionId, ar.compartmentId,
  c.code as constructionCode,
  ac.name as compartmentName
FROM archvizRenders ar
LEFT JOIN constructions c ON ar.constructionId = c.id
LEFT JOIN archvizCompartments ac ON ar.compartmentId = ac.id
LEFT JOIN projects p ON c.projectId = p.id
WHERE p.id = 30010
LIMIT 10;
